  "dagg": "Bakkan waruw dàll la : fa muy dagge doo ko yëg. (,,) Bakkan waru dàll la, buy dagg boroom du ko yëg.",
  "dàgg": ". Nit men naa xeteñ, waaye Yàllaay dàgg.",
