  "jeûner": "'jeûner",
  "jëw": ".\tJakkarloo ku ko mos xam ne jëw a dàq.  .\tJàkkay xobbat jombul ilimaani wunk. (,,) .\tJalu muus janax du ko yër.",
  "jëwam": ". Ku lay mbej ngay fayyu su yaggee mu ba la.  . Ku lekk ab jëwam.",
  "jëwe": "'jëwe",
  "jëwi": "'jëwi",
  "jëwkat": "Ki di def walla ki sàkk 'jëw' (Someone who does...).",
  "jëwu": "Bul war loo di jëwu fas.",
  "jëwub": "'jëwub",
  "jëxëm": "'jëxëm",
  "jéyye": "'jéyye",
  "jib": "Benn lam, du jib daal.",
  "jiba": "Bëgg jiba, duma taxa gaar sama dënn. (,,) Bëgg i ween du ma taxa takk i ngegenaay. (,) Bëgg xaritu pël du ma taxa booti sëllu.   Bëggu yàpp, bu mu la taxa lekk médd.",
  "jibaat": "'jibaat",
