  "naaxu": "Defal boppam 'naax' walla ne ci (Reflexive/Action on self).",
  "naay": "'naay",
  "ñaay": ". Ndab ku ca mënuta sukk sukkin wu jekk, waru caa jéema lekk. (,) . Ndànk-ndànk mooy jàpp golo cib ñaay. (,,,,,,,,)",
  "nab": "Àddina gudd nab tank.",
  "ñab-ñabal": "'ñab-ñabal",
  "ñabaloo": "'ñabaloo",
  "nabb-nabbee": "'nabb-nabbee",
  "nabe": "'nabe",
  "nàcc": "Ku lay añaane xeesaay du la takkal korooj.  . Ku la jam, doo nàcc ! (,)",
  "nàcce": "'nàcce",
  "nàddil": "'nàddil",
  "nafar": "'nafar",
  "nafis": "'nafis",
  "naftu": "Defal boppam 'naft' walla ne ci (Reflexive/Action on self).",
  "nag": "Béjjénu nag jégeñe na lool, waaye bu ñu laalee du sagos boroom. (,)",
  "ñag": "Bérab bu nekk, la fay ñuul, moo fa dib ñag. (,,,) Bérab, la fay ñuul a fa dib ñag.",
  "ñagal": "'ñagal",
  "nagam": "'nagam",
  "ñagam": "'ñagam",
  "ñagas": ". Ñag boo gis dafa wara gëna ñagas la muy ñag, mbaa du ko mëna ñag.  . Ñag bu sore kaw, teewul am picc a ruur.",
  "ñagasal": "'ñagasal",
  "ñagasñas": "'ñagasñas",
  "ñagasoon": "'ñagasoon",
  "ñage": "'ñage",
  "ñàggee": "'ñàggee",
  "nagi": ". Ndëféenaay yóbbuwul nagi mbëtt.  Ndëfeenaay yóbbuwul nagi bët.  Dëféenu yóbbuwul nag i mbëtt.",
  "nagu": ". Nag wu ñuul, ku ca am soow mu weex wara daw ba fattu.  . Nagu naankat, dex a koy tiiñ. (,)",
  "ñagu": "'ñagu",
  "naka": ".\tJëndle la fas wu yaa-biir te duñ(u) la ko gubleel.  .\tJigéen naka takkaayam day, la jikkoom day.  .\tJigéen ay jur lu ne.",
  "naka-su-dul-noona": "'naka-su-dul-noona",
  "naka-su-dul-noonu": "Defal boppam 'naka-su-dul-noon' walla ne ci (Reflexive/Action on self).",
  "nàkk": "Bu la am-am taxa bew, ndax nàkk du wees. (,)",
  "ñàkk": "Am : gore, ñàkk : gore.",
  "ñàkka": "Ñàkka xam mbaam a waral ngay fóon wàqu gannaaw wa.  Ku xamul mbaam mooy fóon we wa.",
  "nàkkal": "'nàkkal",
  "ñàkkal": ". Yomb day tax nga ñàkkal faayda lu am faayda.  . Yomb fey na naajo, ba wes ko.",
  "ñàkkam": "'ñàkkam",
  "ñàkkandoo": "'ñàkkandoo",
  "ñàkkatuleen": "'ñàkkatuleen",
  "ñàkke": ". Ku naan bay jayax, dangaa yemul cim ndox.  . Ku naar di sa gan booba nga ñàkke sa gan.",
  "ñàkkee": ".\tGopp bu nekk ci biir ba muy romb a tax muy bey.  .\tGor, bu ñàkkee, fàttaliku bor. (,)",
  "nàkki": "'nàkki",
  "ñàkki": "'ñàkki",
  "ñàkkoo": "Ku am kuddu du lakk, walla bu lakkee, di cuune.  . Ku am nit ñi, ñàkkoo dara. Ku ñàkk nit ñi, amoo dara. (,)",
  "ñàkkoon": "'ñàkkoon",
  "ñàkkoona": "'ñàkkoona",
  "ñàkkooni": "'ñàkkooni",
  "nàkku": "Defal boppam 'nàkk' walla ne ci (Reflexive/Action on self).",
  "ñàkku": "Defal boppam 'ñàkk' walla ne ci (Reflexive/Action on self).",
  "nàkkub": "'nàkkub",
  "ñàkkub": "'ñàkkub",
  "ñàkkul": "Boroom karaw gu ñuul ñàkkul dara.",
  "ñàkkula": "'ñàkkula",
  "ñàkkuleen": "'ñàkkuleen",
  "ñàkkum": "'ñàkkum",
  "ñàkkuma": "'ñàkkuma",
  "ñàkkuñu": "Defal boppam 'ñàkkuñ' walla ne ci (Reflexive/Action on self).",
  "nal": "'nal",
  "ñal": ". Su ñu nee : “na xob yépp yëngu”, paftan taxul ñuy wax.  . Su picc geddee ab déeg, dafa ñal ag suux. (,)",
  "nalatu": "Defal boppam 'nalat' walla ne ci (Reflexive/Action on self).",
