  "naw": "Boo déggee “jaar bëgg naw sëb”, newul ñu boole kook moom togg.",
  "ñaw": ". Ku bëgge taxa xar sab dënn, ñaw ko dina la jaaxal. (,) . Ku bëggul gaana, ba kook wéñam.",
  "ñawaale": "'ñawaale",
  "ñawal": "'ñawal",
  "ñawante": "'ñawante",
  "nawe": "'nawe",
  "ñawe": ". Wax, ab xottiku la, kenn ku ne, yaa xam noo koy ñawe. (,,,) . Wax daaneelul bëstul.",
  "ñaweel": "'ñaweel",
  "ñaweesu": "Defal boppam 'ñawees' walla ne ci (Reflexive/Action on self).",
  "nawet": "Lu waay rendi, ca suba, ba ngoon ci yoxoom lay nàcc.  . Lu waay wax cib nawet, cab toolam la ko gise. (,)",
  "nawetoo": "'nawetoo",
  "ñawka": "'ñawka",
