  "saxyaayu": "Defal boppam 'saxyaay' walla ne ci (Reflexive/Action on self).",
  "say": "Àddina ñett a ci gën : àjjana biti, ak weerteewlu ak mëneek say dëkk, ak ku la gis bëgg la.",
