  "taxawaalukat": "Ki di def walla ki sàkk 'taxawaalu' (Someone who does...).",
  "taxawaat": "'taxawaat",
  "taxawaay": ". Yuqamtiku yokk nab taxawaay, waaye yàgg caa jafe.",
