  "waccunu": "Defal boppam 'waccun' walla ne ci (Reflexive/Action on self).",
  "wadd": ".\tGawar gu di dawal fasam, mbaxanaam wadd te jotu ko for ?  .\tGaynde bëggul mbuum, yàpp lay dunde. (,,,)",
